CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 18, 1957, pg. A12, reads: "Party Guests - These young people all had a good time at the birthday party of 'Mickey' Bass Jr., age 14, which was held at the Loendi Club recently. The honoree is seated in the first row center. Miss Ida Mae Mauney gave the party for 'Mickey.' - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Mickey" Bass Jr. surrounded by young women and men for 14th birthday party in Loendi Club
